# TCL VMD Script to analyse secondary structure of given protein.
# Based on ramachandran plot. PSI v/s PHI
#
# Authour   : ANJI BABU KAPAKAYALA
#           : C/O Prof.Nisanth N. Nair
#           : IIT KANPUR, INDIA.
